{"tid":1178994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人根本未準備好","createTime":"2019-05-30T20:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T00:28:01.000Z","uid":150609,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"715013fd86dd4f640caea3b3dcda1f72767b802d","tid":1178994,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"講到咩終極一戰生死存亡<br />\n咁你地為呢件事付出左d乜<br />\n<br />\n冇付出代價 點會有成果<br />\n<br />\n香港人 又係走精面 精人出口笨人出手 等運到 求神仙打救<br />\n唔付出 但就想要收穫<br />\n希望侵侵做野 國際施壓 林鄭突然轉性 上帝打救 佛祖打救  <br />\n請問香港人付出了什麼<br />\n你地講幾句野 就要人地外國侵侵出手做餐死<br />\n吃力不討好  香港人就unun 腳坐收成果<br />\n <br />\n合理咩？<br />\n<br />\n繼續馬照跑舞照跳 準時返工  送終條例過唔過<br />\n對你地都係冇影響  一樣日日睇tvb睇倚天 就滿足了"},{"pid":"c2c819b9824af8bcd957efa2bd58b8126766e86c","tid":1178994,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T22:17:59.000Z","msg":"係，唔知樓主掌上壓操到幾多下準備好未。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a3e87fadd4cedca449361221f22a18ca027792","tid":1178994,"uid":8605,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T22:25:51.000Z","msg":"樓主一語道破 港豬根本死不足惜<br />\n<br />\n自己冇覺悟 出去唱幾句今天我都算<br />\n<br />\nOn9到走去篤灰指罵果d有覺悟既義士用暴力<br />\n<br />\n連自己想爭取d咩都唔知 仲ff人地歐美列強係冇利益情況下幫香港<br />\n<br />\n我真係建議你地班和理非收手 唔好害d熱血易衝動既香港同胞去送死"},{"pid":"802067e3253553fb17e714af2723b454abe74dc4","tid":1178994,"uid":24989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"果日遊行睇怕都係會和平散去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b55ad1c7d1c13b7c393f8694d81843249644dd","tid":1178994,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T23:35:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔不願面對既事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e05fa15d8ceddc102780369f644bad11d54af2f","tid":1178994,"uid":186072,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:03:33.000Z","msg":"和平散去就緊架啦<br />\n你唔係覺得啲連登仔會同你博命啊<br />\n人始終都係自私<br />\n出黎一日半日就大大聲話自己有出過力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有後續行動個個就要返工不了<br />\n再哩係屋企做鍵盤戰士啦"},{"pid":"2fc469bac0f3538d76676b5acbf2121982b40eec","tid":1178994,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:05:08.000Z","msg":"只有共產黨先會呃你「未準備好」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3DgSiKNYZLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3DgSiKNYZLI&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=3f8853de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3DgSiKNYZLI</a>"},{"pid":"db921c91256d011f165fddebf777a59183c93b74","tid":1178994,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"有咩計劃"},{"pid":"04656af51f0df3c416044fb645417cf4b02bbddb","tid":1178994,"uid":216396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"歷史上有邊一件革命係完全準備好？"},{"pid":"3d767c8467326027cb4bd8db184923050841e0b6","tid":1178994,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛/ 消極撚/ 分化撚死全家啦</span></span>"}]}